OL,5, Striking rail workers need to accept   
OL,6, reforms to see their pay increase, the 
OL,7, transport secretary has said.          
OL,9,FRMT union members are holding a series 
OL,10,Fof strikes over the festive period     
OL,11,Fwhile trying to negotiate more money to
OL,12,Fmatch rising inflation.                
OL,14,FBut Mark Harper said workplace reforms 
OL,15,Fwere the only way to "free up" funding 
OL,16,Fto do this.                            
OL,18,FThe RMT called on Mr Harper to         
OL,19,F"facilitate" negotiations on a new pay 
OL,20,Fdeal between the union and rail bosses.
